<p><a href="/signalcharm/">“Signal Charm”</a> is a short electronic fiction piece I developed in <a href="http://www.scotthutchins.com/">Scott Hutchins</a>’ Twitter Fiction and Future Forms course, offered under Stanford’s <a href="http://creativewriting.stanford.edu/">Creative Writing</a> program.</p>

<p>The piece presents a fictional narrative through an interactive hypertext format built using HTML, CSS and jQuery. You can view the full piece <a href="/signalcharm/">here</a>.</p>

